<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <!-- Meta Tags -->
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index.css">
        <title><%= bot.name %></title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- Header -->
        <%- include('header'); -%>

        <!-- Main Body -->
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center head">
            <h1><b>Notes. Quick, Simple, Safe.</b></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center subtext">
            <p>The one bot who takes note and doesn't keep track of them. (In a good way)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="container">   
            <div class="container pt-10 custom-1">
                <img class="custom-image" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/895689976417779792/899610697716105246/notedemo1.png" alt="A note sent by NoteFold">
                <h3 class="align-self-start"><b>Send notes straight to your DM's.</b></h3>
                <p>By using a set of complicated algorithms, we have created a bot so good at making notes, we gave it ⭐⭐ gold stars instead of ⭐!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="container pt-10 custom-2">
                <img class="custom-image" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/895689976417779792/899619578164965416/notedemo2.png" alt="A note sent by NoteFold">
                <h3 class="align-self-start"><b>Full Markdown Support.</b></h3>
                <p>Because we ain't fancy, any Markdown Discord supports, we also support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="page-footer font-small footer-dark pt-9">
            <div class="footer-copyright text-center py-3">© GateDev 2021:
            <a href="https://notefold.gatelogic.me"> NoteFold.GateLogic.me</a>
            </div>
        </footer>

        <!-- JavaScript Stuff -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.3.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>